<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空说得对。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都应该回家，不用去西天取经了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要回我的洞里去，美美地睡一觉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒准备要走。悟净抓住了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你疯了？”他看着悟空，“我们不能回家！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”悟空说，“我不是真的说要回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我真的很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我告诉师父很多次妖怪的事情了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可他从来不相信我！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他听我的，他就不会被妖怪抓走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹气。“我们得知道妖怪把他带到哪里去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我问一下这里的土地神。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空闭上了眼睛开始念着什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵风轻轻吹过，土地神出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，孙悟空。”神仙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是这里的土地神。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的师父被妖怪抓走了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们知道那妖怪肯定是这里的妖怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我们不知道他住在哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊。”土地神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的师父很可能是被红孩儿抓走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是个非常邪恶的妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的洞穴就在那山顶上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>土地神指着附近的一座山说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不能去那里。”土地神继续说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“红孩儿非常厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他父亲是牛魔王，也非常厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的脸上出现了笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大笑道：“这真是个好消息！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人都吃惊地看着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么说是个好消息？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“牛魔王是我的老朋友了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在大闹天宫之前，和一群魔王做了朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王是我的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我只要告诉红孩儿我是谁，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他就一定会马上放了唐僧的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个人与土地神道别，向山上走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们到了山顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>附近有一个洞穴，洞门紧闭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空敲了敲门。“开门，红孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要跟你谈谈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门开了，红孩儿走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”红孩儿高傲地问，“你想要干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你抓走了我们的师父唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空说，“快放了他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿哼了一声。“我不会放了唐僧的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要吃了他，然后长生不老。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在在我发火之前，你们最好赶快走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“孩子，你还不知道你在和谁说话吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是美猴王孙悟空，是你父亲的老朋友。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在乎你是谁。”红孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你们所有人，马上离开这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇摇头，装出一副失望的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我本想和平地解决这个问题的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从耳朵里抽出了金箍棒。红孩儿大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得我会怕你那个小小的兵器吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这金箍棒可是天庭的宝贝。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是用来测量海洋的。这宝贝很厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我让它做什么，它就会做什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挺起了胸膛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快放了唐僧，否则我就毁了整座山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也有件厉害的兵器。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿说，“我让你看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打了一下自己的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鼻孔里冒出了烟，嘴里喷出了火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，整座山都烧起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>